{"tid":838242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★iOS 12屏幕限制時間 已被普通7歲小孩破解！","createTime":"2018-09-27T03:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T02:56:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0528efd7a9bf0696ba646fd387c2d8af87e01734","tid":838242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"第一個，也是最明顯的一個，孩子們只要在父母設置的時間截止之前把設備的時間改為更早的時間，就能玩更長時間。而Reddit網站上的一位用戶表示，他的孩子發現了新的辦法。<br />\n<br />\n該網友表示，在iOS 12發布之後，他通過家庭共享限制了7歲兒子使用設備的時間，有幾天他覺得孩子一直在玩，但是他並不知道為什麼。終於，他的兒子說出了原因。<br />\n<br />\n這位機智的孩子在遊戲被鎖定之後，前往App Store通過雲圖標重新下載了遊戲，這樣就繞過了父母設置的限制。家長可以關閉安裝應用選項來避免這一問題，但是這樣也會阻止應用更新，包括安全更新，所以這並不是一個好的解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n其他孩子則通過設置一個隨機限制密碼來阻止父母對他們的遊戲時間進行限制。為了避免麻煩，一些父母覺得採用一些古老的措施，當他們覺得孩子需要休息的時候，就讓孩子交出iPad。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/385/474.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F385%2F474.htm&d=2ZXDsFvQquetjzfk29FMlY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9273178d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/385/474.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e863afc3e92d1cb11a59653d8e8bbde0055213f7","tid":838242,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abda50554fc945542c3e90dc719d764e7a8b5c63","tid":838242,"uid":52215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾屎果<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a2779bdb6d480635c23b93984ddbfb55345882","tid":838242,"uid":17738,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T03:38:17.000Z","msg":"最有效古老方法: 細路交出iPad <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 